Ling Yue!

149
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:39,640
Ling Yue!

150
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,320
Ling Yue!

151
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,720
-Princess.
-Are you alright?

152
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,400
-Sir!
-Don't be afraid.

153
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:51,080
-Go and hide first. Don't be afraid.
-Sir!

154
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,760
-Sir!
-Go now.

155
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,920
-Quick.
-Are you alright, Sir?

156
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:57,800
