-Sir!

157
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:01,280
Help!

158
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:03,360
Help!

159
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,040
-Princess.
-How dare this scoundrel...

160
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,520
