161
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,960
Arrest him!

162
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,800
Quick!

163
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:16,600
-Step aside! Princess.
-I was sleeping just now.

164
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,840
Then I saw someone walking up to me
and tried to take advantage of me.

165
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:21,520
